      "parameters": {
        "width": 1664,
        "height": 896,
        "content": "## 📌 YouTube Ideas from Dumpling AI + GPT-4o\n\nThis workflow triggers when a new YouTube video is added to a Google Sheet.\n\n**Branch 1 – Collect Data**\n1. 📄 Trigger on new video in sheet  \n2. 🔁 Loop over rows (one at a time)  \n3. 📝 Get transcript (Dumpling AI)  \n4. 💬 Get comments (Dumpling AI)  \n5. 🔃 Extract and merge comment text\n"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
